Supergirl TV Talk 2×06: “Changing” w/ Director Larry Teng!

15 Nov 2016
Podcasts Supergirl TV Talk

This week on Supergirl TV Talk, Frank and Tim are joined by episode 6 director Larry Teng for his second appearance on the podcast! They chat about Larry’s experience directing “Changing.” Parasite, Guardian, and more. It’s a packed episode and we hope you enjoy it.
